To create an XPI file use the following command :
    zip -r simplenote-0.1.xpi chrome chrome.manifest defaults install.rdf

Drag and Drop onto Firefox OR use File->Open File menu, to install 

Debugging:
==========
To see debug messages, set browser.dom.window.dump.enabled to true in about:config

On Windows, start firefox with "-console" commandline option
On other OS, starting firefox from terminal is enough.
